HEADWORD: Telary
<hw>Te"la*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>telaris</ets>, fr. L. <ets>tela</ets> a web. See <er>Toil</er> a
snare.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to a web; hence, spinning webs;
retiary.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Pictures of <xex>telary</xex> spiders.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
